{"tid":985580,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[百屌系列] 覺唔覺d小巴無得禁鐘落車好撚反智？","createTime":"2019-01-17T17:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T13:30:04.000Z","uid":52658,"like":7,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"42ee030ad810ce6f2383f1a76910762557ff78ed","tid":985580,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T17:04:47.000Z","msg":"今日我 連登奧米加愛麗絲唔屌陳詠謙住<br />\n我要屌柒而家d垃圾小巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母d戇鳩小巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日坐車尾<br />\n屌你老母我把聲已經細<br />\n架西小巴D屌你老味引擎聲同收音機聲完美地蓋過我把聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連續叫左三四次嗌啦咁 個司機先聽得到我講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母馬亞木專請埋d聾啞人士做司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過呢樣唔重要<br />\n而家已經2019年 你無到站提示同預計報站不特止<br />\n仲要無得禁鐘<br />\n一係d鐘就壞鳩晒既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全係同時代脫節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地希臘咁撚窮 d公車都有得禁鐘啦<br />\n你老味香港真係垃鳩圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申純粹今日只係喉嚨痛同失聲唔想叫到咁大聲<br />\n並不是唔敢叫有落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d13f95fd981822083315f1fcb5b6652bf4d24a5","tid":985580,"uid":172959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T17:05:33.000Z","msg":"其實有"},{"pid":"1de306fb65b8b257ac0d5f0f212883ef30f07a3b","tid":985580,"uid":38795,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T17:09:12.000Z","msg":"有d線有"},